PARAM_CONCURRENCY_LEVEL - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for level of concurrency i.e. number of concurrent threads; default is 1
PARAM_INPUT_FILE - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for name of input file (with construction and statement to prove, described in GCLC or XML format, or with polynomial representation of geometry problem in XML format); if omitted then theorem from internal memory will be used for proving; extension is optional; if extension is omitted then default will be applied that corresponds to given input format; parameter 'i' will determine format of input file
PARAM_INPUT_FORMAT - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for format of input file: can be O (for internal OGP XML format for constructions), A (for XML format for algebraic form of geometric problem); G for GCLC format; default is O
PARAM_LOG_LEVEL - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for log level; default is "B" - basic (log errors, warnings and infos); also can be "E" (only errors), "W" (only warnings and errors), "I" (same as basic), "D" (basic + debug) and "N" (none i.e. turn off logging).
PARAM_OUTPUT_FILE - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for name of output file; default is "output"; extension is determined by output format if not explicitly set (can be '.xml' or '.tex'); only base file name (without extension) is kept in this parameter
PARAM_OUTPUT_FORMAT - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for format of output file: can be X (for XML), L (for LaTeX); A (for all) and N (for none - report will not be created; proving will be faster); A is default
PARAM_PROVER - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for method for proving; default is "W" (Wu), and can also be "G" (Groebner)
PARAM_SPACE_LIMIT - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for space limit as maximal number of terms in single polynomial obtained during proving process
PARAM_TIME_LIMIT - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter for time limit in milliseconds for proving single theorem (default is 10 seconds)
PARAM_VERBOSE - Static variable in class com.ogprover.main.OGPParameters
Parameter with no specific value assigned; simply if exists in command line its value will be true; otherwise false; if it is true, then all log messages will be printed to standard output as well; especially info will give messages about actions taken by prover
